    {
      "text": "Noon is a Action-Puzzle game, published by Micro Cabin, which was released in Japan in 1998.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Noon (also known as noontime or midday) is 12 o'clock in the daytime.\nSolar noon is the time when the Sun appears to contact the local celestial meridian. This is when the Sun reaches its apparent highest point in the sky, at 12 noon apparent solar time and can be observed using a sundial. The local or clock time of solar noon depends on the date, longitude, and time zone, with Daylight Saving Time tending to place solar noon closer to 1:00pm.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
